ygData.messageBody:
have to agree with Tony B on that. had a tnt2 ultra, and decided to try one
out. (didnt really think it would make that big a difference) There isnt
much difference in it, Untill you go above 1024X768, and then it really
starts to shine. (about 20fps faster)

James
